{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"orientationchange","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>orientationchange</code>&nbsp;이벤트는 장치의 방향이 바뀔 때 호출 된다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"General info","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"specification\">Specification</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/screen-orientation/#event-handlers\" rel=\" noopener\">Screen Orientation</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Event</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Screen</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"default_action\">Default Action</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">None</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Note that \"orientationchange\" and screen.orientation are unprefixed in the following</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// code although this API is still vendor-prefixed browsers implementing it.</span>\nscreen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"orientationchange\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"the orientation of the device is now \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>orientation<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"General info","id":"general_info"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"}],"summary":"orientationchange 이벤트는 장치의 방향이 바뀔 때 호출 된다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: orientationchange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window: orientationchange イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"orientationchange","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Window: orientationchange event","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/window/orientationchange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/window/orientationchange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event","title":"orientationchange"}],"pageTitle":"orientationchange - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}